<span id=task_a2g_dispatcher-class></span><h2 id='task_a2g_dispatcher-class-'>TASK_A2G_DISPATCHER Class</h2>
<pre>
Inheritance : The TASK_A2G_DISPATCHER Class inherits from the following parents :
BASE
    `-- FSM
        `-- DETECTION_MANAGER
            `-- TASK_A2G_DISPATCHER
</pre>

<h4> Attributes </h4>

<ul>
<li><a href="#set_group-class-">SET_GROUP</a> SetGroup : The groups to which the FAC will report to.</li>
<li><a href="#detection_base-class-">DETECTION_BASE</a> Detection : The DETECTION_BASE object that is used to report the detected objects.</li>
<li><a href="#mission-class-">MISSION</a> Mission</li>
</ul>
<span id=task_a2g_dispatcher-new-mission-setgroup-detection></span><h3 id='task_a2g_dispatcher-new-mission-setgroup-detection-'>TASK_A2G_DISPATCHER:New(Mission, SetGroup, Detection)</h3>
