<span id=task_a2g_dispatcher-processdetected-detection></span><h3 id='task_a2g_dispatcher-processdetected-detection-'>TASK_A2G_DISPATCHER:ProcessDetected(Detection)</h3>
<p>Assigns tasks in relation to the detected items to the <a href="#set_group-class-">SET_GROUP</a>.</p>

<h4> Parameters </h4>

<ul>
<li>#TASK_A2G_DISPATCHER self</li>
<li><a href="#detection_base-class-">DETECTION_BASE</a> Detection : The detection created by the <a href="#detection_base-class-">DETECTION_BASE</a> derived object.</li>
</ul>

<h4> Returns </h4>

<ul>
<li><u>Boolean</u>  Return true if you want the task assigning to continue... false will cancel the loop.</li>
</ul>
